<tr><td><strong>Primary focus</strong></td><td>Cognitive enhancement, focus, neuroprotection</td><td>Anxiolytic, mood stabilization, stress reduction</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Derived from</strong></td><td>ACTH (adrenocorticotropic hormone)</td><td>Tuftsin (immune peptide)</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Core mechanism</strong></td><td>BDNF/NGF upregulation, dopamine modulation</td><td>GABA modulation, serotonin metabolism</td></tr>
