<tr><td><strong>Anxiety reduction</strong></td><td class="y">Moderate (via enkephalinase inhibition)</td><td class="g">Strong (primary effect)</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Cognitive boost</strong></td><td class="g">Direct (primary effect)</td><td class="y">Indirect (via anxiety reduction)</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Best for</strong></td><td>Demanding study, high-stress work, neurorecovery</td><td>Generalized anxiety, chronic stress, emotional balance</td></tr>
