<div class="d-t">
  <div class="s">The Stack That Works</div>
  <p>Many users combine both peptides. Semax provides the raw cognitive horsepower while <a href="/articles/selank-complete-guide">Selank</a> removes the anxiety and mental noise that can undermine focus. The combination produces a state of calm clarity that neither peptide achieves as effectively on its own. For a detailed guide on this pairing, see our <a href="/articles/cognition-stack-semax-selank-dihexa">cognition stack guide</a>.</p>
</div>

<!-- ========== STACKING ========== -->
<hr class="sep">
<h2>Stacking Semax With Other Compounds</h2>

<p>Semax's mechanisms make it a strong candidate for stacking &mdash; the goal is choosing compounds that complement its action or address areas it doesn't primarily cover.</p>

