<!-- ========== SIDE EFFECTS ========== -->
<hr class="sep">
<h2>Side Effects and Safety</h2>

<p>Semax has a favorable safety profile backed by decades of clinical use in Russia. Most users experience no side effects at recommended doses. When side effects do occur, they tend to be mild and transient.</p>

<table class="tbl">
<thead><tr><th>Side Effect</th><th>Frequency</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
